Package com.fauna.constants

Class ResponseFields

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fauna.constants.ResponseFields
  • public final class ResponseFields
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines constants for field names in responses returned by the Fauna Core HTTP API.

    The ResponseFields class centralizes commonly used JSON field names in Fauna responses, making it easier to reference them consistently and preventing hard-coded strings throughout the codebase.
